{"tid":897282,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人永遠呼吸都好似吸唔夠氣咁","createTime":"2018-11-10T18:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T09:03:13.000Z","uid":59566,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3de366d29980367694c4a5a938ddfb5984933be1","tid":897282,"uid":59566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"其實幾年前已經有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先係個鼻好似索極都唔夠力吸氣咁<br />\n跟著又要長期手動呼吸<br />\n但係用個口又要勁大力咁索先至好似吸得夠氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家仲要唔知點解成日都會有啲小動作例如用力谷一吓個肺再噴一吓氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似痴線佬咁到底有冇辦法解決"},{"pid":"3ee3a00d6c0a7956c02d3522e67c5efb2ad49584","tid":897282,"uid":120556,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"樓主運動下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57af7712269f2cb21ef937cad694f9659373adc","tid":897282,"uid":4519,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:48:37.000Z","msg":"屌你，睇完個post變左手動呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f4f9eaba1961258091ac871b937d621cedf45e","tid":897282,"uid":205534,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:48:41.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣睇到呢個po就手動呼吸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57350eb4517ac56c27a496c8555907d4f02969d5","tid":897282,"uid":59566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee3a00d6c0a7956c02d3522e67c5efb2ad49584","tid":897282,"uid":120556,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20